{"tid":628781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨時六四紀念館下周五開幕","createTime":"2018-04-14T07:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T07:55:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5c61db21198c585a986d0186c5d801008542d0","tid":628781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361287?_ga=2.11649844.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361287%3F_ga%3D2.11649844.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=o8Ll8V75HeyJumkgqsKAXf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=792bf567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361287%3F_ga%3D2.11649844.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=432f84d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361287?_ga=2.11649844.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：臨時六四紀念館下周五開幕 - 李八方<br />\n1.4K<br />\n專欄專論<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2F64.jpg&h=ffa1b74c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臨時六四紀念館亦會喺下周五開幕。支聯會網站圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n距離一年一度六四燭光悼念集會有個幾月，但多得新任人大常委譚耀宗公開話邊個講結束一黨專政，就係違憲、甚至冇得參選，令市民更關注今年六四燭光晚會。其實支聯會今年嘅六四悼念活動已經開始，而臨時六四紀念館亦會喺下周五開幕，而今年以改革開放40年與六四為主題，仲有六四解密檔案展出。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會副主席麥海華話希望藉主題，帶出改革開放40年同六四事件之間關係，佢話改革開放固然改變中國，但同時亦引起好多經濟、社會文化、環保、甚至宗教等問題，呢啲問題亦同六四嘅出現有關，希望有助市民更深入認識六四前因後果。<br />\n<br />\n今次紀念館亦有一個六四解密檔案展覽。麥話六四事件至今29年，近年海外唔少有關六四嘅檔案陸續解密，有助市民更了解六四真相，好似六四死難人數，中國官方話幾十人，但好多外國政府解密檔案就話以千人計，今次展出正好畀市民更完整咁了解六四真相。<br />\n<br />\n麥話出年係六四30周年，希望今年係最後一年搞臨時六四紀念館，出年可以有新嘅永久六四紀念館。"},{"pid":"97e2b89ba5d21a66b3bf07173e4b972a982d6b15","tid":628781,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"380660c7b12a8574bd69c50b7b0ec8d3a577fc78","tid":628781,"uid":5477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:22:19.000Z","msg":"Support <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d95473d26488dc8c3d77ff5d832e1cbe4ee48d","tid":628781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>人民不會忘記</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.g